ploys.description:
Whenever a friendly HERNKYN YAEGIR operativo is fighting, or has a Conceal order and is retaliating,
add 1 to the Atk stat of its melee weapons (to a maximum of 4) and they have the Balanced weapon rule;
if the weapon already has that weapon rule, it has the Ceaseless weapon rule instead of Balanced.

Use this firefight ploy when it's your turn to activate a operativo amigo. Select one friendly HUNTER CLADE LEADER operativo and one other ready friendly HUNTER CLADE operativo visible to and within 3" of that LEADER operativo;
activate one of them as normal. When that first operativo amigo you activate is expended, you can activate the other operativo amigo before your opponent activates.
When that other operativo is expended, your opponent then activates as normal. Whenever you use this ploy, you cannot select more than one HUNTER CLADE SICARIAN operativo.

Use this Firefight Ploy when an operativo enemigo is shooting or fighting a friendly RATLING operativo (excluding OGRYN or BULLGRYN) and you are allocating a die to block.
If it is a éxito normal, it can block one unresolved éxito crítico;
if it is a éxito crítico, it can block two unresolved successes (normal or critical).
